  "title": "Drafter",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description &amp; Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>*Responsible for maintaining project drawings and submissions</p>\n<p>*Coordinate, review and verify drawings including owner &amp; maincontractor’s drawings to ensure compliance with design specifications and guidelines.</p>\n<p>*Able to work in a fast-paced environment and both independently and in a team.</p>\n<p>*Supporting the duties as assigned by management.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>*Experienced in AutoCAD 3D and BIM, and able to understand architectural or structural drawings</p>\n<p>*3 years of relevant working experience</p>\n<p>*Well-versed in construction detailing / building regulations.</p>",
